1
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,960
Luckily Mr. Zhu helped out.

2
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:00,200
He talked to your principal.

3
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:00,960
Said you're

4
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,160
a really promising student.

5
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:04,160
Otherwise getting back into school

6
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:05,520
would've been a huge hassle.

7
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:09,479
Once I'm back at school,

8
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:10,680
you'll be here by yourself.

9
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,560
Will you be okay?

10
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,120
Of course I will.

11
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,560
Don't underestimate your mom.

12
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,200
Zhao Pock

13
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,440
read my palm once.

14
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,760
He said I'd

15
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,680
have a turn for the better.

16
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,400
Great luck with mentors

17
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,400
and career.

18
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,360
Zhao Pock?

19
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:29,840
He did a reading for me too.

20
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:31,440
Said I'll become a scientist one day.

21
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:33,200
Total nonsense.

22
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,600
I think his words hold true.

23
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,640
Don't worry.

24
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,360
Ye has paved the way

25
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,880
for us.

26
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,800
Besides, with the salon reopening,

27
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,400
things will get better for sure.

28
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,400
Supporting the whole family

29
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,480
won't be a problem.

30
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:50,840
You've got this?

31
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,360
I've got this.

32
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,720
What are you worried about?

33
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:58,000
Grandma has her wheelchair.

34
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,680
Liu Nian

35
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,120
will help me run the salon.

36
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:01,520
And Cici also lends a hand

37
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,560
out there.

38
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,440
What else could go wrong?

39
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,840
I told you I can handle it,

40
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:07,840
and handle it I will.

41
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,000
You mean it?

42
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,520
Right.

43
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:12,720
I mean it.

44
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:52,960
Mom.

45
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,400
The moon is full tonight.

46
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:07,320
Can I come in?

47
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,560
Sure.

48
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,520
I got foot bath sachets

49
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,680
from Doctor Zhuang.

50
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,320
Soak your feet for some time.

51
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,360
It'll ease the soreness.

52
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,399
You got a new haircut.

53
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,440
Look more like a student now.

54
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,520
Come on.

55
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,960
The water's just right.

56
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,560
This feels amazing.

57
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,800
Like all my energy's flowing free.

58
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:50,840
What are you laughing at?

59
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,720
Looks like cooking pig trotters.

60
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:53,920
You think so too, don't you?

61
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,400
It really does.

62
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:00,600
And the smell

63
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:02,320
is pretty similar too.

64
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,400
Funny you say that.

65
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,480
There's Chinese prickly ash

66
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,760
and cassia twig inside.

67
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,480
So Doctor Zhuang really is

68
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,720
braising pigs' trotters?

69
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,240
He knows what he's doing.

70
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,520
These herbs

71
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:13,000
boost blood circulation

72
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,240
and relax your muscles.

73
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:22,040
Thanks a lot for today.

74
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:23,800
Otherwise,

75
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,280
I'd have

76
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:26,400
struggled badly

77
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,520
after those twenty laps.

78
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:32,760
You didn't have to run all that.

79
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:34,080
I did.

80
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,960
A bet's a bet.

81
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:41,640
It's also

82
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,520
a wake-up call

83
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:45,200
for slacking off lately.

84
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:47,440
What do you mean?

85
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,400
Even with my English score added,

86
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,680
my monthly exam results

87
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:53,520
still aren't enough

88
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,800
for my dream college.

89
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,360
What's more,

90
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,400
when the college entrance exam comes,

91
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,680
Cao Fan isn't my only rival.

92
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,560
So I need to adjust

93
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,760
my study methods

94
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,960
and push myself harder.

95
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:10,120
Do you believe I can make it?

96
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,080
Absolutely.

97
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,720
So sure about that?

98
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:13,560
Why?

99
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:14,640
No reason.

100
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:15,880
I just do.

101
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,280
Alright then.

102
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,480
Do you also believe

103
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,920
that I can get us both

104
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,760
to be admitted to good universities?

105
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:27,640
Well...

106
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,280
I'm not like you.

107
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,200
I haven't studied for years.

108
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,200
Getting into college

109
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:35,680
is almost impossible.

110
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:38,600
Where there's a will, there's a way.

111
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,520
How will you know if you don't try?

112
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:41,440
But you really

113
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,200
shouldn't waste your time

114
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:44,240
on me.

115
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,600
Besides, I'm back at school

116
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,400
not to go to college.

117
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,120
I know.

118
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,000
Just to get a high school diploma.

119
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:52,880
Exactly.

120
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:57,840
Alright.

121
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,520
A bit longer,

122
00:06:58,520 --> 00:06:59,600
they'll really become braised trotters.

123
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,200
Lift your feet.

124
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:08,520
Good night.

125
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,760
Morning, Classmate Xing.

126
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,760
Morning, Classmate Qing.

127
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,160
You look

128
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:29,320
much more proper now.

129
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:30,400
Like I wasn't

130
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,640
proper before.

131
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,440
You used to be an engineer,

132
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,920
now you're a student.

133
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,160
Which do you prefer?

134
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:37,280
Both are fine.

135
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:38,200
Pick just one.

136
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:39,440
Can't I pick both?

137
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:40,920
Don't get carried away.

138
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,600
You've turned

139
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,800
more "E" lately.

140
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,000
You even crack jokes now.

141
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:45,720
"E"?

142
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,640
What do you mean?

143
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,000
Have you done the MBTI test?

144
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:48,880
What's that?

145
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,960
You were totally an introvert before,

146
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,040
but now you're an extrovert.

147
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,560
Introvert, extrovert...

148
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:55,760
I just wanna be a student now.

149
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:56,920
Let's go.

150
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:58,120
Wait.

151
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,400
You're not fully dressed

152
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,040
as a student yet.

153
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,560
Where's your name tag?

154
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:04,880
Forgot to put it on.

155
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:08,800
Let me help you.

156
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:20,840
Done.

157
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:22,360
Is it straight?

158
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:22,920
Yep,

159
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:23,800
perfect.

160
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:25,560
Let's go.

161
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:26,040
Yeah.

162
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:29,080
Nice day today.

163
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,080
What are you listening to?

164
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:54,120
English.

165
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:55,200
Listening practice.

166
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:58,560
Listen with me.

167
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,240
I'm not interested.

168
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:34,440
So?

169
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:35,440
How's it?

170
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,200
Pretty good.

171
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,200
What's the song called?

172
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,360
"I promise"

173
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,400
It's really nice.

174
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,640
Let's listen to another one.

175
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:54,880
Listening practice?

176
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,280
Not for me.

177
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,400
You have to.

178
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:07,400
Fine, whatever you say.

179
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:40,680
Oh, by the way,

180
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:41,320
the...

181
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:41,960
Well?

182
00:13:42,040 --> 00:13:42,600
Getting used to it?

183
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,520
- This uniform is so uncomfortable.
- Ye.

184
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:45,560
Ye.

185
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:48,560
Who's this?

186
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,600
Who else could it be?

187
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:52,640
New sneakers.

188
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:53,800
New haircut.

189
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:55,200
Let's celebrate.

190
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,720
You dare step on my new sneakers?

191
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:01,800
You want your feet kicked?

192
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,840
Don't you know?

193
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:04,040
Step on new shoes

194
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,000
for good luck.

195
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:06,040
Pat a new haircut

196
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,160
for wit and cheer.

197
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:08,720
See?

198
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,400
He doesn't stutter anymore

199
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,160
since you came back.

200
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,800
No kidding.

201
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:14,760
I even planned to

202
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,520
repeat senior year.

203
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:17,400
Don't say such unlucky things.

204
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:19,400
Then I'll tag along with you

205
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,640
and Qing Ye from now on,

206
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,200
study, eat and drink together.

207
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:24,680
I'll stay in school right alongside you.

208
00:14:25,160 --> 00:14:26,600
Oh, stop that.

209
00:14:27,160 --> 00:14:27,800
Is it too late

210
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:29,000
to quit school

211
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:29,960
now?

212
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:32,160
Yep.

213
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:33,560
Yep.

214
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:34,680
Yep.

215
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,400
Wait.

216
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,520
Wait for me!

217
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:37,320
Here.

218
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:38,560
Let's go.

219
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,560
Actually, I really admire Xing Wu.

220
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:52,960
For what?

221
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,960
Few people in Anzi County

222
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:55,920
dare to say no to my dad,

223
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,280
but he did.

224
00:15:00,280 --> 00:15:01,240
That's just how he is.

225
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:03,320
Once he sets his mind on something,

226
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:04,520
he'll see it through

227
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:05,360
no matter what.

228
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:08,200
I wish I could be like him.

229
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,200
Right, Shu Han,

230
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:14,120
don't pick me up after school anymore.

231
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:16,400
Why?

232
00:15:16,920 --> 00:15:17,960
Do you have other plans?

233
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:21,160
I'll stay for evening study

234
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:22,880
and review lessons with Qing Ye.

235
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,440
You must be tired after work.

236
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:26,960
I'll take a taxi home.

237
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:29,080
Call me anytime

238
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:29,960
if anything comes up.

239
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:46,920
Sorry.

240
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:48,960
I can't sign the contract.

241
00:15:49,920 --> 00:15:50,560
Why?

242
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,120
If it's about the pay,

243
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:52,920
I can talk to Mr. Ye

244
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:53,880
to raise it for you.

245
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:54,760
It'll be easy.

246
00:15:55,680 --> 00:15:56,160
No.

247
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,160
It's not that.

248
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,880
I've decided to go back to school.

249
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:02,320
Back to school?

250
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:04,840
Are you serious?

251
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:05,840
Why did you suddenly

252
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:06,640
change your mind?

253
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:10,520
Just wanna get

254
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:12,760
a high school diploma.

255
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,640
Come on.

256
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:17,000
If that was all you wanted,

257
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,160
you'd have gone back long ago.

258
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,120
It's because of Qing Ye, isn't it?

259
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:29,800
I knew it.

260
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:31,840
Spit it out. What's going on?

261
00:16:32,560 --> 00:16:33,760
I want to protect her

262
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,360
and keep her away from trouble.

263
00:16:36,800 --> 00:16:38,040
Let her focus on the exam.

264
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:40,080
Xing Wu,

265
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,080
you care so much about her.

266
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,520
Now you're

267
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:46,960
giving up a job

268
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:47,720
just for her?

269
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:52,520
Fine.

270
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:54,880
But as your friend, I have to say this.

271
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:56,200
Someday

272
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:57,440
Qing Ye will leave here.

273
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,600
She'll leave Zhazhating,

274
00:16:59,040 --> 00:16:59,680
and head for

275
00:16:59,680 --> 00:17:00,840
bigger places.

276
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,000
Maybe she'll even

277
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:03,400
forget this place.

278
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:04,599
I know.

279
00:17:05,319 --> 00:17:06,079
You can only

280
00:17:06,079 --> 00:17:07,280
walk beside her for now.

281
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:08,720
I get that too.

282
00:17:08,800 --> 00:17:09,680
You do?

283
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:10,520
Then what about later?

284
00:17:10,839 --> 00:17:11,560
What about your future?

285
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:19,119
Whether she stays or goes,

286
00:17:19,599 --> 00:17:20,599
whether she remembers here or not,

287
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:22,160
it doesn't matter.

288
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:23,520
I just want her

289
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,520
to get through this time

290
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:27,760
smoothly and safely.

291
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:30,160
I've always had your back.

292
00:17:32,360 --> 00:17:33,320
If you ever get tired of

293
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:35,120
being a student,

294
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:37,120
you're always welcome back again.

295
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:41,120
I'm busy.

296
00:17:41,120 --> 00:17:42,040
You can see yourself out.

297
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:20,000
Qing Ye.

298
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:22,120
Could you do me a favor?

299
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:23,440
Go ahead.

300
00:18:25,560 --> 00:18:26,960
Could you give this

301
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:28,640
to your cousin, Xing Wu?

302
00:18:31,760 --> 00:18:32,680
