336
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,080
Be quiet.

337
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:22,720
Definitely grinding away.

338
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:24,400
I didn't expect Xing Wu

339
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,520
to be this popular

340
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:26,600
