343
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:32,760
Yeah.

344
00:19:32,760 --> 00:19:33,200
Right.

345
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:34,840
Wu just transferred into our class,

346
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:36,280
