348
00:19:39,080 --> 00:19:39,600
He's so...

349
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:40,800
Excellent.

350
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:42,600
Too excellent.

351
00:19:43,280 --> 00:19:44,000
No wonder he's admired

352
