372
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:35,360
Take it.

373
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,120
Get lost.

374
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:39,440
I bought it for Xing Wu.

375
00:21:08,360 --> 00:21:09,040
