405
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:18,000
Take care of your hands.

406
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:32,520
Smells great.

407
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,000
Thanks.

408
00:22:59,160 --> 00:22:59,920
It's supposed to be

409
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:00,840
