413
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:09,280
I'm all alone.

414
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:10,520
I'm leaving. Enjoy your wait for her.

415
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:13,640
Xing Wu,

416
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:14,840
