417
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:15,720
Mine's broken.

418
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:16,640
Could you take a look?

419
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:17,600
Mine too.

420
00:23:17,680 --> 00:23:18,360
Mine as well.

421
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:18,880
Okay.

422
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:20,000
You're so nice.

423
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,200
I'll check them later

424
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:22,440
