425
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,760
Thank you so much.

426
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:25,320
Well.

427
00:23:25,520 --> 00:23:26,040
No problem.

428
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:26,680
Thanks.

429
00:23:43,560 --> 00:23:44,320
Volunteer.

430
00:23:44,520 --> 00:23:45,360
Volunteer.

431
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:46,120
Volunteer. Right?

432
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:47,840
You've got enough vocabulary.

433
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:49,480
English class feels

434
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:50,520
