437
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:08,720
Bye.

438
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:09,520
See you tomorrow.

439
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:10,080
Bye.

440
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:38,760
Fun studying with him, huh?

441
00:24:39,360 --> 00:24:40,800
Enjoy chatting with them, huh?

442
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:44,560
Quite popular.

443
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:46,720
Not bad.

444
00:24:47,120 --> 00:24:48,240
Gotta open them up and take a look?

445
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,400
Of course.

446
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:50,640
And one by one,

447
00:24:50,640 --> 00:24:51,400
