448
00:24:52,040 --> 00:24:52,920
One by one?

449
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:55,400
So it's more than one?

450
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:57,960
Yeah, quite a few actually.

451
00:24:58,320 --> 00:24:58,920
I didn't expect

452
00:24:58,920 --> 00:24:59,800
