466
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:40,520
This way.

467
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:53,520
What do you feel like eating?

468
00:25:54,760 --> 00:25:55,880
Anything is fine.

469
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,440
I'm so full.

470
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:08,240
I'll never

471
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,560
