474
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:13,280
"This dish was great, and that one too."

475
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:18,160
Why is it raining all of a sudden?

476
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:18,720
Come here.

477
00:26:20,040 --> 00:26:21,600
The forecast didn't

478
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:23,160
