479
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:24,160
It just came pouring down.

480
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,240
Probably a passing shower.

481
00:26:25,360 --> 00:26:26,560
Comes fast, goes fast.

482
00:26:27,520 --> 00:26:28,680
