575
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:56,520
It means you're insightful.

576
00:31:58,160 --> 00:31:58,960
Who told you that?

577
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:02,760
Your grandson,

578
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,040
Xing Wu.

579
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:05,680
Don't listen to him.

580
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:24,760
Lanfang.

581
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:27,000
Xing Wu.

582
00:33:29,560 --> 00:33:30,320
Open the door!

583
00:33:30,720 --> 00:33:31,200
Cici.

584
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:31,920
- Lanfang.
- What's wrong?

585
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:32,880
It's an emergency.

586
00:33:34,120 --> 00:33:35,600
Something terrible happened.

587
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,360
