589
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:39,320
Missing?

590
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,000
When did you notice?

591
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:42,080
Just now.

592
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:43,400
Calm down.

593
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,320
Come inside.

594
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:47,560
Easy, easy.

595
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:48,520
Take your time.

596
00:33:49,280 --> 00:33:49,960
What happened?

597
00:33:50,120 --> 00:33:50,920
I scolded him

598
00:33:51,520 --> 00:33:52,640
